  "3295360": {
    "name": "如胶似漆",
    "steam_appid": 3295360,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在小孩哥的混乱房间里开始大冒险！为了防止你们的逃跑他在房间中布下了机关重重的天罗地网，关卡设计越来越不讲理，疯狂旋转的CD，失控的吸尘器，甚至还有离谱的外星科技？！！巧妙地运用地形、合理地协调动作，不过最重要的还是确保你们两人之间“情比金坚”！ （温馨提示：游戏支持在线或本地，但请注意在本地游玩时，确保好您与队友的人身安全，不要相互攻击）</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295360/extras/488aae03b5f3380ad24eaaddd831c53d.avif?t=1769054618\" width=616 height=106 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这款游戏里，“闹掰”从来不是意外——它是一门艺术。试想一下，你们将被强制绑定成一对——你们认为对方是你可靠的“另一半”。当你自信满满地喊着“交给我”，结果一个错误的抬手，就会在“另一半”队友的尖叫中跌落回起点。从物理意义上来说，游戏中你们已经是相伴终生了。但是希望你们在游戏结束后，依旧相亲相爱...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >（PS：当队友伸出“圆手”，说不定ta已准备好看到你紧张的尖叫了）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295360/extras/32d73be2f0429afabb405526e3b75f69.poster.avif?t=1769054618\" width=1170 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295360/extras/32d73be2f0429afabb405526e3b75f69.webm?t=1769054618\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295360/extras/32d73be2f0429afabb405526e3b75f69.mp4?t=1769054618\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295360/extras/f9e96cd7eac8cea5808600ed266472d0.avif?t=1769054618\" width=616 height=106 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与“另一半”展开一场相爱相杀的大逃亡。荡秋千、攀家具、穿越由各种奇怪排列的家具组成的“登天长梯”，可能好不容易扒住的救命稻草，结果是意料之外的陷阱！甚至还有怪异的UFO干扰你们的前行！你们需要默契配合才能通关……考验你们是否是真爱的时候来了。别让你们的感情与攀爬一样坚持不住！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295360/extras/4c9e0932598d2fa747716c30ae5faaca.poster.avif?t=1769054618\" width=1170 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295360/extras/4c9e0932598d2fa747716c30ae5faaca.webm?t=1769054618\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295360/extras/4c9e0932598d2fa747716c30ae5faaca.mp4?t=1769054618\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295360/extras/d7e5d93e12ac0f490bb54e583bd70f01.avif?t=1769054618\" width=616 height=106 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >用将自己的橡胶手紧紧黏住每一个能抓到的物品，合作征服重力的极限攀爬！每一次抓住、荡起、都是一次豪赌！命悬一线时的心跳加速，与即将脱离控制时的尖叫连连，哪怕离登顶只有最后一步，也要屏住呼吸！因为可能一点的失误，就要从起点开始——不过，坠落本身不也是一种心跳加速？勇敢跃出第一步，下一秒你就知道失败有多欢乐！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295360/extras/165ade36700d7ee8cb1e16d421bf8307.poster.avif?t=1769054618\" width=1170 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295360/extras/165ade36700d7ee8cb1e16d421bf8307.webm?t=1769054618\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295360/extras/165ade36700d7ee8cb1e16d421bf8307.mp4?t=1769054618\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295360/extras/a57a733f85f1bca646b4ba617933051e.avif?t=1769054618\" width=616 height=106 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >气急败坏的小孩儿哥，阴险的招式有的呢。当你们终于找到了合适的节奏，觉得有点进展，终点就在眼前的时候，突然一只大手朝你们呼啸而来。不过别忘了——每一次被他整蛊的瞬间，都是你们合作的最佳考验。当你被风扇吹飞，队友伸出那只圆圆的手；当你们在空中相视一笑、再一次坠落时，那一刻的默契与狼狈，或许正是最真实的“真情告白”。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295360/extras/cbf88d3190ae29fb551ef8f003eab433.poster.avif?t=1769054618\" width=1170 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295360/extras/cbf88d3190ae29fb551ef8f003eab433.webm?t=1769054618\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295360/extras/cbf88d3190ae29fb551ef8f003eab433.mp4?t=1769054618\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
